{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "cb97749c-8a0e-46bd-8d52-5ec2d684e67b", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/cb97749c-8a0e-46bd-8d52-5ec2d684e67b@2.pkg/1772597645894/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597646811", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/cb97749c-8a0e-46bd-8d52-5ec2d684e67b@2.pkg/1772597645894/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597646811"}, "identifier": "cb97749c-8a0e-46bd-8d52-5ec2d684e67b", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>正确答案：A</p>\n\n<p>A（正确）：强调青少年要主动掌控而非被动接受算法推送，符合\"工具论\"核心观点；</p>\n\n<p>B（错误）：未否定AI价值，而是强调主体性；</p>\n\n<p>C（错误）：观点本身承认网络价值，只是强调使用边界；</p>\n\n<p>D（错误）：与题干\"做主人\"的积极态度相矛盾。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<ol>\n\t<li>（原创）在AI深度融入日常生活的背景下，\"数字原住民\"一代如何与网络相处引发热议。某教育专家指出：\"青少年应当做智能设备的主人，而非算法的附庸。\"这一观点（　　）</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n", "title": "（原创）在AI深度融入日常生活的背景下，\"数字原住民\"一代如何与网络相处引发热议。某教育专家指出：\"青少年应当做智能设备的主人，而非算法的附庸。\"这一观点（　　） ", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/cb97749c-8a0e-46bd-8d52-5ec2d684e67b@2.pkg/item.json?v=1754618728342", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "tit